                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The increase to shield capacity provided by Redirection is applied after rank bonuses from levelling up a warframe."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Redirection",
                  "pageId": 17682,
                  "revisionId": 2699781,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example, if a maxed Redirection is applied to a level 30 Frost Prime , the base shield capacity (550) is increased by the +100 base shield rank bonus, giving 650. This total is multiplied by 2 (+100% Shield bonus from redirection), giving a grand total of 1300 shield capacity."
                }
              }
